---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Shipping Policy | PosturePro"
  description="Free US shipping on all PosturePro orders. 3-5 business day delivery."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Shipping Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Free US Shipping</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        All orders shipped within the United States qualify for FREE standard shipping.
        No minimum purchase required.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Delivery Times</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>US Standard:</strong> 3-5 business days (FREE)</li>
        <li><strong>US Express:</strong> 1-2 business days ($9.99)</li>
        <li><strong>International:</strong> 7-14 business days (varies by location)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Order Processing</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Orders are processed within 1-2 business days. You will receive a tracking number
        via email once your order ships.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">International Shipping</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We ship to most countries worldwide. International shipping rates and delivery
        times are calculated at checkout based on your location. Please note that
        international orders may be subject to customs duties and taxes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Questions?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@posturepro.com" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">support@posturepro.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-8 text-green-600 hover:underline">‚Üê Back to Shop</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
